OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Ftonight with clear skies for a while,
OL,7,Fthough some patchy low cloud arriving
OL,8,Ffrom the east later. Temperatures will
OL,9,Ffall under the clear spells to give a
OL,10,Fpatchy rural frost in sheltered
OL,11,Flocations.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FAfter a chilly start, it will
OL,14,Fbe another warm day with light winds.
OL,15,FBright at first, but skies turning
OL,16,Fincreasingly hazy with a small chance
OL,17,Fof the odd light shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
