OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers possible on Monday, otherwise
OL,7,Fit looks dry with some warm sunny
OL,8,Fspells and variable cloud at times.
OL,9,FTurning a little breezier on
OL,10,FWednesday. Some chilly nights.
